WEBVTT

00:00.333 --> 00:02.333
Previously on Greenleaf.

00:02.358 --> 00:04.019
She's still not willing
to come to a meeting.

00:04.043 --> 00:06.643
This may be a situation
where you need to step up,

00:06.678 --> 00:08.045
<i>lead, be the man.</i>

00:09.838 --> 00:11.909
- Sorry to interrupt.
- No interruption.

00:11.963 --> 00:12.827
Jabari Johnson.

00:12.863 --> 00:14.095
Who told you I did this?

00:14.131 --> 00:15.618
Mr. McCready's father, Henry.

00:15.657 --> 00:18.068
- What did Henry say, exactly?
- That you paid him to burn down.

00:18.092 --> 00:21.895
First Baptist Church in 1983,
the one Darryl James died in.

00:21.930 --> 00:23.240
I don't know what kind of deal you cut

00:23.264 --> 00:25.131
to get out of jail with this story,

00:25.629 --> 00:26.524
you're going back.

00:26.560 --> 00:27.781
I'm not going anywhere.

00:27.819 --> 00:29.384
Everybody at school knows.

00:29.419 --> 00:30.739
Is that why you took those pills?

00:30.764 --> 00:32.798
Yeah. Why isn't he in jail?

00:37.188 --> 00:41.808
Right here is the new pastor
of Triumph Two,

00:42.484 --> 00:44.117
Jacob Greenleaf.

00:44.152 --> 00:46.684
- What do you have against me?
- You killed my daddy.

00:46.730 --> 00:48.163
You're Darryl James's boy?

00:48.199 --> 00:49.698
<i>We got a little trouble</i>

00:49.733 --> 00:50.881
over at Triumph Two with the excavation.

00:50.902 --> 00:53.589
The water table's higher than
the Geological Survey indicated.

00:53.625 --> 00:55.949
My life's not about you, Pop.
It's about me.

00:55.985 --> 00:58.204
- He doesn't respect me.
- I respect you.

